Aye, this would be the Haven... and I would be Liani.  The rules are fairly simple... Don't molest the staff, that includes the pixies... livestock stays in the yard, with the exception of the tigers but then who can keep a cat from going where it pleases?... and of course... NO Gnomes allowed.<br>
<br>
Other than that, my regulars are a bit of a rowdy bunch, hope you dont mind... <br>
<br>
careful of the side room there <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  she crooks a thumb at the now empty private bar room with the sturdy door that bolts from the OUTSIDE</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> unless you like to fraternize with a passel of drunken dwarves...<br>
<br>
Pretty much anything you could possibly want can be found here... help yourself to the fridge, the bar, the pond out front... though be careful there as the mermaids and sirens are sometimes a bit overly playful... and if there is anything you would like but cant seem to find, or dont WANT to bother finding for yourself, just ask a pixie.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Liani's face splits into a playful grin</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
And now that the formalities are complete... welcome to the Haven... make yourself at home!<br>
